data.description: Nestled in the heart of North Beverly, step inside to a bright and inviting classic Georgian boasting 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths.  This beautiful home features hardwood floors throughout, tons of sunlight, and a recently refinished kitchen with stainless steel appliances.  The spacious living room is flooded with natural light flowing to the dining room which showcases 2 large French doors. The Dining room opens to a deck overlooking a large fully fenced in yard perfect for entertaining and relaxing with a built in fire pit.  The house is complete with a finished basement featuring a wood burning fireplace and plenty of storage.  The side drive leads to the back yard with large storage shed.  Enjoy the convenience of this prime beverly location, close to the award winning Blue Ribbon Christ The King School, Kellogg Elementary School, Dan Ryan woods & forest Preserve, METRA, restaurants and parks.
